name: DR-165
description:
As an assessor,
  I want to be able to see a list of nearby trainers on the assessment request summary page while I am booking assessment for a trainer,
  so that I can maximise efficiency of assessment bookings.

steps.name: that I have licence.ndors.org.uk page opened
I am on Pick a course page
I click Request assessmet button against trainer I want to book an assessment
I will be taken to Request Assessment Summary page
I check Include this Trainer for a trainer
The system will include the selected trainer in the booking request
